# 8. ストイックは永遠に

Haruka: Thank you all for watching the stream and giving me your support today, everyone!
Haruka: We didn't win in the end... But I'm glad we were able to complete that course as a team.
Haruka: That being said, I plan to continue training in order to learn how to do what I couldn't today.
Haruka: And don't be afraid to come give it a try the next time you visit Nonogi Park.
Comments: <Congratulations! You were awesome today!> <I wish I could form a team with you, Haruka...> <Please do more training videos!>
Airi: Anyway, thanks again for sticking around until the end, you guys! We'll see you during our next stream!
Shizuku & Minori: See you again! Bye bye!
Haruka: Thank you both again for doing such a good job today!
Tsukasa: Of course! We really gave this event everything we had!
Haruka: Yes, we did...
Haruka: I'm so sorry. If only I hadn't gotten stuck at the end...
An: Haruka...
Tsukasa: What are you saying, Kiritani?! I honestly still don't know how you were able to make it to the finish line!
Akito: We also lost some time along the way, so it was a team effort in that sense.
Tsukasa: Also, I'm glad we trained so hard. It's the reason we succeeded when quite a few groups failed to finish in the end.
Tsukasa: So, please allow me to thank you again for being such a wonderful leader.
Haruka: No, I should be the one thanking you two. This ended up being a really great experience.
Haruka: This event reminded me of the importance of not giving up. So, thank you.
Akito: You're welcome.
Tsukasa: Still, I wasn't expecting all the groups that finished to receive a special prize...
Akito: Special one-time passes that give us free entry to the training area.
Minori: Wait, really?!
Airi: Nice! That means we get to try out the latest machines and equipment!
Shizuku: Hehe. What a wonderful prize. Thank you, Haruka!
Haruka: *Nod* I hope we can find a day to train as MORE MORE JUMP! and...
Girl: H-Haruka!
Haruka: Huh? Me?
Girl: Yes! I, uhh... I wanted to tell you something...
Haruka: Okay, what would you like to tell me?
Girl: U-Umm... I thought what you did today was really cool!
Girl: I don't do very well during P.E. and stuff, but I feel like trying a little harder to become more like you now.
Girl: So... Thank you, Haruka! I promise to do my best during the next “Everybody MORE MORE DANCE!” stream!
Haruka: Oh...
Haruka: Hang on... Are you the one who posted that one comment about not being as athletic as you'd like?
Girl: ...! You remembered?!
Haruka: Hehe. Of course I did. Thank you for always being so supportive.
Haruka: We promise to keep doing streams that everyone can benefit from.
Haruka: So let's keep doing our best together.
Girl: ...! Okay!
Girl: Anyway, bye bye!
An: Now then... I'm sure you guys are all starving after working up such a big sweat.
An: So, let's go grab some barbeque! I just learned about this really great place the other day!
Tsukasa: Barbeque? That does sound good.
Airi: We can have a party to celebrate your guys' efforts. So, mind leading the way...?
Haruka: Sorry, I'll pass.
Shizuku: Wait, why?
Haruka: Because...
Haruka: I still need to do my evening run.
An: What?
An: H-Hang on a second! You're still gonna run?! But you just finished competing!
Haruka: I know. I'm really tired, which I think is the best time to run that extra mile.
Minori: Th-That's Haruka for you... She's not about to budge!
An: No, we gotta get her to go! Akito, Tenma, say something...
Akito: Actually, I might also go for a run. I feel like exercising a little more.
Tsukasa: Me too! After all, we're used to doing runs in the evening now!
Tsukasa: So, let's all keep doing our best!
An: Wait, you guys...
Haruka: Okay. I hope we get to do this again soon.
Akito: Me too.
An: What?! You guys are seriously gonna run right now?!
Shizuku: They really plan on giving this day everything they have...
Airi: We could follow their example, but I feel like they're going a bit overboard.
An: Oh, Haruka...
An: Not so fast! I wanna run with you!
Haruka: Huh?
An: After listening to you guys talk, I also feel like running now, you know?!
Minori: W-W-Wait, I wanna run too!
Haruka: Are you sure? My plan was to do four kilometers.
An: Four kilometers...?!
An: N-No, I can do that!
Minori: M-Me too...! Let's go!
Haruka: Hehe. Okay. Then, follow me!
